+      <strong>Objective: Switching from FTP transport listener to mail
+      transport sender</strong>
+    </p>
+    <p>
+      <strong>Prerequisites:</strong><br/> You will need access to
+      an FTP server and an SMTP server to try this sample.
+    </p>
