+
+                </p>
+            </subsection>
+            <subsection name="Pre-requisites">
+                <p>
+                    <ul>
+                        <li>
+                            Deploy the SimpleStockQuoteService in the sample Axis2 server and start Axis2
+                        </li>
+                        <li>
+                            Start Synapse using the configuration numbered X (repository/conf/sample/synapse_sample_X.xml)
+                            <div class="command">
